data.value: 1 - Chose a RPX/RPL to load (it will decompress the RPX/RPL file) 2 - If the RPX/RPL is in the list select it else chose "Others games" 3 - Put the address of the value you want to change (If the RPX/RPL is in the list the adress are the same of IDA.
